Guideline for Installation
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

A. Installation with code::blocks cbp file:
	A1. Make sure you have installed cbp2make first.

	A2. Generate Makefile for code::blocks project using cbp2make

		cd ./project
		cbp2make -in ${PROJECT_NAME}.cbp -out Makefile

	A3. Then modify the Makefile, append the include path for ${INC}, library 
	    for ${LIB}
		
		INC = -I ../include
		LIB = -l${YOUR_LIB}

B. Install log4cxx:
	1. download:
		a) log4cxx: http://logging.apache.org/log4cxx/
		b) apr: http://apr.apache.org/download.cgi
		c) apr-util: http://apr.apache.org/download.cgi
	2. Install apr
		tar xjf apr-1.3.3.tar.bz2
		cd apr-1.3.3
		./configure --prefix=strategy_core/third
		make
		make install
	3. Install apr-util
		tar xjf apr-util-1.3.4.tar.bz2
		cd apr-util-1.3.4
		./configure --prefix=strategy_core/third --with-apr=strategy_core/third
		make
		make install
	4. Install log4cxx
		tar xzf apache-log4cxx-0.10.0.tar.gz
		cd apache-log4cxx-0.10.0
		./configure --prefix=strategy_core/third --with-apr=strategy_core/third --with-apr-util=strategy_core/third
		make
		make install

